# Phase 35.2 · AI Trader Final Polish

Repository: `cvsz/zdash`

Execution profile: DeepSeek V4 Flash Free / fast free coding model.

Goal:
Finalize the AI Trader Simulation Control Plane for release readiness while keeping it strictly simulation-only and routed through existing zDash safety systems.

Do not add live trading. Do not add broker execution. Do not add external ML dependencies.

---

## Safety invariants

- AI Trader remains simulation-only.
- Paper trade remains dry-run only.
- No live trading button exists in UI.
- No broker order execution is added.
- Do not bypass `TradingService`.
- Do not bypass `ExecutionEngine`.
- Do not bypass `SignalValidationService`.
- Do not bypass Guardian risk checks.
- Do not bypass RBAC, audit/event logging, or dry-run mode.
- Every signal metadata must include `simulation_only=true`.
- Every signal metadata must include `risk_policy.live_execution_allowed=false`.
- Every visible AI Trader UI must show simulation-only / not financial advice / no live execution language.

---

