---

## Backend requirements

### Strategy registry

Verify deterministic strategies exist and are simulation-only:

```text
trend_momentum_v1
mean_reversion_v1
volatility_breakout_v1
conservative_guarded_v1
```

Each strategy should expose:

```text
id
name
description
risk_profile
min_candles
default_min_confidence
supported_symbols
supported_timeframes
simulation_only=true
```

### Feature engine

Verify no external ML dependency is used.

Features should include:

```text
close
fast_ma
slow_ma
ma_delta
momentum_3
momentum_7
volatility_pct
atr_proxy
volume_ma
volume_ratio
trend_state
volatility_state
candles_analyzed
warnings
```

Malformed/insufficient candle data must not crash normal requests; return hold/warnings.

### Service behavior

Verify:

- `generate_signal(...)` returns `TradingSignal`.
- insufficient candles return hold.
- confidence below threshold returns hold.
- strategy compare does not execute orders.
- `paper_trade(...)` forces `dry_run=true`.
- execution goes through `TradingService.execution_engine.execute(...)`.
- all outputs include safety metadata.

### API behavior

Verify endpoints:

```text
GET /api/ai-trader/status
GET /api/ai-trader/strategies
POST /api/ai-trader/signal
POST /api/ai-trader/compare
POST /api/ai-trader/paper-trade
```

RBAC:

```text
status/strategies/signal/compare require Permission.READ_TRADING_SIGNALS
paper-trade requires Permission.RUN_DRY_RUN_TRADING
```

Responses must include:

```text
simulation_only=true
safety_notice
model_version
risk_policy
warnings where applicable
explanation where applicable
```

---

## Frontend requirements

Verify `AITraderSimulationCard` includes:

- strategy selector
- symbol input
- timeframe input
- min confidence input
- generate simulation signal button
- compare simulation strategies button
- run dry-run paper trade only button
- model version display
- generated direction
- confidence
- validation state
- execution state
- strategy comparison table
- simulation-only banner
- no live trading button

UI text must be clear:

```text
Simulation only
No live broker execution
Not financial advice
dry-run only
```

---

## Tests

Ensure tests cover:

```text
insufficient candles returns hold
malformed candles do not crash
up trend gives buy or hold
down trend gives sell or hold
compare returns ranked decisions
paper trade always dry_run=true
metadata includes simulation_only=true
metadata risk_policy.live_execution_allowed=false
frontend card renders simulation controls
frontend compare table uses non-ambiguous assertions
no live button exists
```

Add missing tests only where coverage is absent.

---

## Validation

Backend targeted:

```bash
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
python -m pytest -q tests/test_ai_trader_service.py tests/test_ai_trader_phase34.py
```

Backend full:

```bash
cd backend
source .venv/bin/activate
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
python -m ruff check app tests
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
python -B -m pytest -q
```

Frontend targeted:

```bash
