source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh
nvm use 20
npm test -- AITrader.test.tsx
```

Frontend full:

```bash
cd frontend
source ~/.nvm/nvm.sh
nvm use 20
npm test
npm run build
```

---

## Allowed changes

Allowed:

- deterministic AI Trader bug fixes
- metadata completeness fixes
- API response shape fixes
- frontend label/safety copy fixes
- tests for AI Trader behavior
- docs updates

Not allowed:

- live trading
- broker integration
- external ML packages
- model API dependencies
- bypassing existing trading safety services
- hidden execution path

